meanings: [Suffix] forming nouns of condition or quality, from nouns or adjectives

h.a.d. headwear produces multifunctional bandanas that can be used as a cap, desert scarf, headband, scarf, hairnod etc. They come in many different colors and patterns and were used mostly by race drivers. It has now become a trend to wear them everywhere.
